extendedInfo.description: You're mobile and so are we! As you navigate HCAA's Executive Forum, we've developed mobile tools to help you stay connected no matter what! We have designed our mobile App to help you personalize your online experience at HCAA's Executive Forum. You can manage your schedule and flag the booths you want to make sure you visit. While you're in sessions, you can take notes directly in the App. Thinking about where to go in Vegas for dinner? We've got great recommendations for you; and reservations are just a click away in this app. Your dashboard keeps your schedule front and center while connecting you to the social media buzz. Download HCAA's EF13 App today! Keywords: HCAA, Executive Forum, TPA, Self Funding insurance, Self Funding Conference
